{"tid":1190140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文化遺產大澳龍舟遊涌上演　居民祈求驅疾平安","createTime":"2019-06-07T07:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T07:20:25.000Z","uid":92376,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ff64a810a52bd33ab2ddb38eecdef49b1f178d","tid":1190140,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190607/photo/bkn-20190607142210033-0607_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190607150834\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190607142210033-0607_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190607150834&h=53902013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大澳今日(7日)舉辦一年一度的國家級非物質文化遺產項目「龍舟遊涌」活動，拖着載有小菩薩神像的艇，巡遊大澳水道，為大澳水陸居民祈求平安。 <br />\n<br />\n此活動百多年來從未間斷，負責的3個大澳傳統漁業行會包括「扒艇行」、「鮮魚行」及「合心堂」，進行「龍舟遊涌」和龍舟比賽，龍舟健兒早上率先進行採青及接神儀式，先到楊侯廟及關帝廟等寺廟接神，用神艇將代表菩薩的小神像接到龍舟會的龍躉。 <br />\n<br />\n其後3個傳統漁業行會分別派員扒龍舟，進行「遊涌」。龍舟隊伍沿途焚燒金銀衣紙，寓意祭祀水中幽魂。水道兩旁的棚屋居民會朝着龍舟拜祭，祈求閤家平安、驅除疾病。龍舟隊伍隨後作表演賽及送神儀式，用小艇將神像送返廟宇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190607/photo/bkn-20190607142210033-0607_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190607150834\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190607142210033-0607_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190607150834&h=0b8e893b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190607/photo/bkn-20190607142210033-0607_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190607150834\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190607142210033-0607_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190607150834&h=8aabec1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190607/photo/bkn-20190607142210033-0607_00822_001_04p.jpg?20190607150834\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190607142210033-0607_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20190607150834&h=bbb3db6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64387c85e985401bd41961ded4041e55da674a63","tid":1190140,"uid":172840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:16:43.000Z","msg":"廢老節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7019501450df29be2a0ce45f81fb0c5c98e5f5d2","tid":1190140,"uid":118781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:20:25.000Z","msg":"棚屋d 馬桶就係直落下面d水到, 你地就喺堆棚屋中間玩水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}